![Critical values for the t-distribution with x degrees of freedom (α= 0.05). The dashed red line shows the Z critical value (i.e. df = ∞).](t_CI_files/figure-html/fig-tcrit-1.png){#fig-tcrit fig-align='center' width=95%}
